{"tid":929365,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"各科分數平均　邊緣考生蝕底","createTime":"2018-12-05T13:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T11:39:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6336b0a608ff6dbdc4df765ee34fd7ed32770529","tid":929365,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:36:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181203/20560110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F20560110&d=YyekKvfmAwBtsofWRRxBFRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=0b9e8856\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F20560110&h=93f8146b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181203/20560110</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月03日 <br />\n<br />\n各科分數平均　邊緣考生蝕底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181203/large/1202yiu1002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181203%2Flarge%2F1202yiu1002.jpg&h=d58fdc12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳嘉敏（左）建議各院校日後須統一並盡早公佈調整計分機制，讓學生有足夠時間更改選科策略。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大學聯招星期三截止申請，但港大上月才公佈今年更改聯招入學計分方法，即考生在文憑試科目考到5、5✽或5✽✽級的考生，將分別獲加0.5分、1分及1.5分。學友社學生輔導中心總幹事吳寶城認為，港大的新計分方法，將影響分數平均的邊緣考生入讀港大機會，也會打亂應屆考生的讀書及選科策略，「若分數平均嘅考生想入港大，變相有壓力要谷某啲科有5✽或5✽✽」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港大改計分制　七成DSE生呻太遲公佈　影響聯招選科策略<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n團體︰宜考完試再評估<br />\n<br />\n應屆文憑試（DSE）考生，本周三前（12月5日）須決定「大學聯招辦法」（JUPAS）的首論選科。學友社學生輔導中心總幹事吳寶城稱，港大新計分方法，將影響分數平均的邊緣考生入讀港大機會，也會打亂應屆考生的讀書及選科策略。<br />\n<br />\n他舉例，在新計分方法下，一名考生若考獲5科5級，如入讀港大，可獲額外加2.5分，即共27.5分；若另一個考生同樣考5科，當中兩科考獲5✽✽，其餘為443，即可獲加3分，即有28分，「舊計分制下兩個考生都係25分，但分數平均嘅邊緣考生就最蝕底&hellip;&hellip;因為新計分方法下，有拿✽✽嘅考生獲加分，人哋加得多，你加得少，可能入到（港大）變成入唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n吳寶城稱，考生選科時可根據個人興趣、出路等作考慮因素，又指雖然港大更改計分方法，但建議考生現階段應專注考試，待明年考試結束後，才評估個人成績後再選科，「考完試再評估有冇邊啲科比較突出，如果有某啲科有機會攞5✽或5✽✽，可以揀港大嘅選擇多啲，如果唔係咪保守啲揀其他。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者譚靜雯  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港大改計分制　七成DSE生呻太遲公佈　影響聯招選科策略<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n七成超市蛋為「籠屋蛋」　含菌風險高25倍"},{"pid":"77310ba1db3ce3b6fac31a377be4abb5dd2928f9","tid":929365,"uid":80183,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"我地港大唔受廢人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e863fe9711fd092e14eac3408960f78210699f9","tid":929365,"uid":34757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cc97ac42e575b929e5fb549e098e0ca3dbfe878","tid":929365,"uid":2002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:56:10.000Z","msg":"後門咪人到港大囉-.-"},{"pid":"da220d0c62a9d6f3812673152b19d5a81f57ad24","tid":929365,"uid":127929,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"77310ba1db3ce3b6fac31a377be4abb5dd2928f9","tid":929365,"uid":80183,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"我地港大唔受廢人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Cut4nN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Cut4nN.png&h=5960be84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sre56Be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSre56Be.png&h=4daf1028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRfH8PB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRfH8PB.jpg&h=fbc38d96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f579a271219df7e644341cc4ed3477d9e10dcd95","tid":929365,"uid":180156,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"無星學咩人入一大"},{"pid":"938d5c16755f7d5ca6d8197bd3e78b0278dfa148","tid":929365,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018